title: Jaco Pastorius kicking Robert Trujillo's ass
fulltitle: Jaco Pastorius kicking Robert Trujillo's ass

description: Robert Trujillo is talking about his first encounter with Jaco Pastorius - true jazz punk. Robert was busy in London with all-star Mass Mental (Armand Sabal-Lecco, Whit Crane, Benji Webbe) and also his documentary Jaco was receiving its UK premiere on Saturday 12th March at London Bass Guitar Show 2016 in Olympia.
